
'''BATUK'''
Qeybta Tababarka Ciidamada Qalabka Sida ee Kenya (BATUK) waa cutub taageera tababarka ciidanka Britishka ee ku yaala [[Kenya]] iyada oo loo marayo heshiisyada wadashaqaynta muddada dheer ee wadankan.


* Peace Training Support Centre
* The Nanyuki Show Ground (NSG)
* Kahawa Barracks, Nairobi
* Kifaru Barracks, Nairobi
* Archer's Post Training Area
* Dol Dol Training Area
* International Mine Action Training Centre

'''Xaalada hadda'''

Wasaaradda Difaaca ee Britain (UK) waxay sii wadaysaa Heshiiska Wadajirka ah ee Iskaashiga Gacanta ee Dowladda [[Kenya]] oo ilaa lix Gurracan oo Ingiriis ah ah (10,000 oo shaqaale ah) sanadkiiba waxay qaadan karaan tababar afar toddobaad ah oo laga fulinayo Dhulka Great Rift Valley ee [[Kenya]]. Fududeynta Goobta Laishipia ee Gobolka Laikipia kuma jirto UK oo sidaas darteed fursad gaar ah u leh askarta Britishka si ay xirfad ugu helaan tababarka.

Jimicsiga waxaa maamula Waaxda Tababarka Ciidamada Kenya ee ku yaala xerada Kifaru ee Nairobi, iyo Nanyuki Showground Camp (NSC), oo 200 km waqooyiga caasimadda. Intaa waxaa dheer saddex kooxood oo Royal Engineers ah oo fuliya mashaariicda mashaariicda mashaariicda mashaariicda, halka laba shirkadood oo ka tirsan shirkadaha caafimaadka ay bixiyaan gargaarka caafimaadka aasaasiga ah ee bulshada rayidka ah. [[Ingiriiska]] ayaa sidoo kale siinaya fursado tababar oo muhiim ah oo ka socda [[Boqortooyada Midowday]] (UK) si ay u helaan xubno ka tirsan Ciidamada Difaaca [[Kenya]] waxaana ay qabanqaabiyaan tababaro iskudhaf ah Ciidamada Difaaca Kenya. Laga soo bilaabo 2015 ayaa UK waxay sidoo kale siin doontaa taageero weyn oo ku wajahan caqabadaha Kenya ee ka dhanka ah Al-Shabaab, oo ay ku jiraan u diridda shaqaalaha Britishka ah si ay u siiyaan taageerada Taageerada Ciidamada Difaaca Kenya, iyo tabarucidda tababbarada la-dagaallanka argagixisada ee Booliska Kenya iyo ilaaliyayaasha xuduudaha.

Tababarka Ciidanka [[Ingiriiska]] ee Kenya ayaa qayb ka ahaa muranadii diblomaasiyadeed ee ka dhexeeya Ingiriiska iyo Kenya ee 2013-2015. Inkasta oo Heshiiska Iskaashiga Iskaashiga ee u dhaxeeya UK iyo Kenya ay u baahan yihiin Ciidanka Britishka si ay u hoggaansamaan Sharciga Kenya, ciidamada Britishku waxay jecel yihiin in ay isku dayaan askar sida uu qabo sharciga milatariga UK. Inkasta oo Askarta Britishka ah ay sharcigeen sharciga Kenya, haddana waxay ku jireen wax ka mid ah degaanka sharci darrada ah. Xukuumadda Kenya waxay ku doodeysaa in ciidamada British-ka ay ku lug lahaayeen dambiyo aan qallafsaneyn oo ka dhacay Nanyuki. Intaa waxaa dheer, Ingiriiska Bases iyo maraakiibta militariga ma aysan dabooli karin marka laga reebo dhammaan hay'adaha Kenya. Labadan khilaafaad ayaa sababay iska horimaadyo sannadka 2013. Laikipia County waxaa ka dhacay sharci darro iyo qalab militeri oo Ingiriis ah ayaa badanaa lagu soo rogay tuugo ballaaran inta lagu jiro layliyada. Dagaalka ayaa yimid kadib markii kooxo hubaysan oo aad u hubaysan ay u muuqdaan in ay geysteen xad-gudub ay sameeyeen meelihii tababarka milatari muddadaas oo ay ku jireen jimcihii Bryan George Maddison oo xubin ka ahaa kooxdii tababarka BATUK ku toogtay oo dilay mid ka mid ah 12-kii weerar ee is-difaacay. Iyadoo bilayska Nanyuki ay sheegeen in Maddison uu si macquul ah u dhaqmay, qaar ka mid ah siyaasiyiinta maxaliga ah ee Kenya iyo Qareenka Guud ee [[Kenya]] ayaa ugu baaqay Maddison in lagu maxkamadeeyo [[Kenya]]. Maddison waxaa lagu xiray Kenya, khilaafkuna waa uu sii daayay. Jawaabta Ingiriiska ayaa si muuqata u baari doonta fursado kale oo tababar ah oo ka socda Tansaaniya iyo Jabuuti taasoo keentay in dareenka Ingiriisku ka baxo uu keeni doono dhaawac aad u weyn oo dhaqaale ah iyo lumitaanka adeegyo caafimaad oo bilaash ah oo ay bixiso Wasaaradda Difaaca Ingiriiska.

Dhaawacyada sababay rayidka ka soo jeeda beelaha nool ayaa sidoo kale sabab u ahaa xiisadda; dhaqdhaqaaqayaashu waxay sheeganayaan in 50 qof oo Kenyan ah (inta badan xoolo dhaqatada) ay dileen ciidamo aan loo baahneyn ilaa iyo 1945-kii. Dawladda Ingiriiska ayaa ka jawaabtay in kuwa dhaawacmay ay doorteen si sharci daro ah oo ay u galaan goobo tababar oo calaamad ah, ayna soo jeedinayaan in ayan jirin ciidamo aan loo baahnayn oo ay ciidamada Kenya ka baxayaan goobaha. [2]

Dhibaatada dhabta ah ee khilaafka ayaa ah midka ugu macquulsan ee lagu xukumay doorashada madaxweynenimada Kenyatta ee 2013-ka sababtoo ah dambiyada ku lugta leh ee ka dhanka ah bani'aadamnimada ee ka dhanka ah isaga oo jooga Maxkamadda Caalamiga ah ee Dambiyada. Inkastoo Britain ay tahay maal-gashadeeda ugu weyn ee Kenya, [[Kenya]] ayaa ogolaatay Siyaasadda Bariga Bari ee isku dayaya in ay soo jiidato Maalgashi Shiinaha ah.

Wadahadaladii u dhaxeeyay David Cameron iyo Madaxweyne Uhuru Kenyatta ayaa ku soo biiray heshiis bishii Sebtembar 2015 kaas oo ah goobaha militariga ee Britishka loo qaaday kormeer, askar British ah ayaa lagu tijaabin doonaa Kenya (ma ahan qasab maaha sharciga Kenya) in la caddeeyo aagga hore ee sharciga ah iyo askarta Kenya waxaa lagu soo bandhigi doonaa fursado tababareed oo dheeraad ah gudaha UK iyo ciidamada Britain ee Kenya. Heshiiskaani wuxuu ka turjumayaa kuleylinta guud ee xiriirka ka dhaxeeya Madaxweynaha iyo Kenyatta.
